item.title: All Episodes - The Landing Page Sessions - Unbounce
item.description:
All Episodes - The Landing Page Sessions - Unbounce

The Landing Page Sessions are all about finding the "squeaky wheel" in your marketing campaigns. We look at the whole picture-landing pages, emails, ads, remarketing-and demonstrate how to increase your conversion rates. Want a chance to have your page on the show? Submit your LP!

item.title: The Ultimate Growth Hacking Sourcebook /// Rocketshp
item.description:
The Ultimate Growth Hacking Sourcebook /// Rocketshp

What's that? "Yet another compendium of Atari-era marketing tactics!" we hear you softly groan to yourself. "Aren't there enough guides on growth hacking floating about the internet already?", you then rightfully ask aloud. "There's blah and blah and blah, and then there's also blah, blah, blah". Agreed.
